    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"let yourself be still\"... that sounds nice, but it's not really possible. i walk into a room and i can feel people looking through me. the shame is everywhere. it's not just a bad phase, it's like the person i was is actually dead. how do you even start over when there's literally nothing left to build on?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
